<!-- SS About Astrology — rebuilt from star-story-theme/sections/icon-text.liquid -->
<!-- Settings hardcoded from product.json icon_text_CTy3M7 -->
<!-- Icon images: Frame_8721.svg -> ss-icon-frame-1.svg (note: doesn't exist), Frame_8722 -> ss-icon-frame-2.svg, etc. -->

<div class="ws-icon-text-shopify-section">
    <h1 style="text-align: center; padding: 20px 20px 60px 20px;">About Astrology</h1>
    <div class="ws-icon-text-container">

        <div class="ws-icon-text-container-item">
            <img class="ws-icon-text-img" src="{{ 'ss-icon-frame-2.svg' | asset_url }}">
            <div class="ws-icon-text-inner">
                <div class="ws-icon-text-header">What Is Astrology</div>
                <div class="ws-icon-text-content"><p>Astrology is the study of the movements and relative positions of celestial bodies interpreted as having an influence on human affairs and the natural world. It offers insights into personality, relationships, and life events through the lens of the stars and planets.</p></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-icon-text-container-item">
            <img class="ws-icon-text-img" src="{{ 'ss-icon-frame-2.svg' | asset_url }}">
            <div class="ws-icon-text-inner">
                <div class="ws-icon-text-header">How Does Astrology Work</div>
                <div class="ws-icon-text-content"><p>Astrology works by analyzing the positions of the planets and stars at the time of your birth, known as your natal chart. This chart acts as a cosmic map, revealing patterns and tendencies that shape your character and destiny.</p></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-icon-text-container-item">
            <img class="ws-icon-text-img" src="{{ 'ss-icon-frame-3.svg' | asset_url }}">
            <div class="ws-icon-text-inner">
                <div class="ws-icon-text-header">The Science</div>
                <div class="ws-icon-text-content"><p>Astrology is rooted in ancient traditions and observational practices. It combines precise mathematical calculations and rich symbolic meanings to interpret the influences of celestial bodies on human life, providing a unique perspective on personality and destiny.</p></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ws-icon-text-container-item">
            <img class="ws-icon-text-img" src="{{ 'ss-icon-frame-4.svg' | asset_url }}">
            <div class="ws-icon-text-inner">
                <div class="ws-icon-text-header">How Astrology Can Help You</div>
                <div class="ws-icon-text-content"><p>Astrology can offer guidance and perspective, helping you understand your strengths, challenges, and potential paths. It provides a deeper awareness of your inner self and can be a valuable tool for personal growth, decision-making, and finding harmony in various aspects of your life.</p></div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

